metadata.name: "Exodus"
metadata.description:
GonSoku is a heroic figure who has been fighting for humanity since the world was destroyed by an atomic war. His spaceship "Exodus" is his vessel of hope as he travels through the cosmos in search of a new home for mankind. 
This NFT captures the essence of his courageous journey, showcasing a vivid and abstract artwork with dynamic lines and colors. His determination and perseverance is an inspiration to us all, and his mission to keep humanity alive will never be forgotten.

No Commercial Rights.
